wrapScienceJ.wrapImaJ.core

Class VoxelShort

  • java.lang.Object
    • wrapScienceJ.wrapImaJ.core.VoxelShort

  • public class VoxelShort
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a voxel with its integer coordinates in the three dimensions stored as shorts on 2 Bytes. This class can be used for memory intensive storage of voxel's coordinates since these coordinates generally don't take high values so that they fit in a short.
